Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.82,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It smells wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Here you go... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:11.54,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Seems like you're not a fan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Too bitter? Want some sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:18.72,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Adding some milk might help remove some of that bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.10,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Or would you like something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.32,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t like milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:27.63,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I see... I'm sorry. I didn’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.50,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Want me to grab you some juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:35.02,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:41.04,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I didn't like tea when I was your age either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:46.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I mentioned that there's lots of different kinds of tea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,There are teas that I don't like too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean I won't drink them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:57.14,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,but I have my own tastes for which types of tea I like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.97,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What's your taste in drinks, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:03.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh - is there any reason you don't like milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.04,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It makes my stomach rumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.17,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,(giggling)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:11.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Funnily enough, I was the same way when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.54,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Especially when they served milk at school lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.00,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I can drink it now, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.84,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,To be honest, I really like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Can you have stomach-friendly milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:25.28,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What kind of milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:30.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I forget the name of it, but there's a type of milk that doesn't make your stomach rumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:34.88,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It's for you, and other kids who had the same issue I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:38.72,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you ask your mother about it, I'm sure she can find you some!
